left to right direction
skinparam usecase {
 BackgroundColor LightBlue
 BorderColor DarkBlue
}

actor User as U

rectangle \"User Actions\" {
 usecase \"Sign In\" as SignIn
 usecase \"Register\" as Register
 usecase \"OAuth Google\" as OAuthGoogle
 usecase \"OAuth Facebook\" as OAuthFacebook
 usecase \"Logout\" as Logout
 usecase \"View\" as View
 usecase \"Toggle Follow Other User\" as ToggleFollowOtherUser
 usecase \"Edit User Profile\" as EditUserProfile

 usecase \"Login Provider\" as LoginProvider
 usecase \"Authorize Access\" as AuthorizeAccess

 usecase \"View Profile\" as ViewProfile
 usecase \"View Video\" as ViewVideo
 usecase \"Comment\" as Comment
 usecase \"Like\" as Like
 usecase \"Share\" as Share

 usecase \"Error Message\" as ErrorMessage
 usecase \"Change Picture\" as ChangePicture
 usecase \"Edit Credentials\" as EditCredentials
 usecase \"Delete Account\" as DeleteAccount

 U --> SignIn
 U --> Register
 U --> OAuthGoogle
 U --> OAuthFacebook
 U --> Logout
 U --> View
 U --> ToggleFollowOtherUser
 U --> EditUserProfile

 SignIn ..> ErrorMessage : Wrong Credentials
 SignIn --> LoginProvider : <<extend>>
 Register --> LoginProvider : <<extend>>
 OAuthGoogle --> LoginProvider : <<extend>>
 OAuthFacebook --> LoginProvider : <<extend>>
 LoginProvider --> AuthorizeAccess : <<extend>>

 View --> ViewProfile : <<include>>
 View --> ViewVideo : <<include>>
 ViewVideo --> Comment : <<include>>
 ViewVideo --> Like : <<include>>
 ViewVideo --> Share : <<include>>
 View --> AuthorizeAccess : <<extend>>

 ViewProfile --> ToggleFollowOtherUser : <<include>>

 EditUserProfile --> ChangePicture : <<include>>
 EditUserProfile --> EditCredentials : <<include>>
 EditUserProfile --> DeleteAccount : <<include>>
}

@enduml
